column1: # attribute -- name: Average GNP per Person
column2: description: GNP (Gross National Product) is the total value of products and services generated by all residents. This amount is divided by the whole population to create an average amount per person for the country. It is expressed in international dollars so that it reflects the same purchasing power as the US dollar.
